sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import "./Discovery.css"; import IMG from '../imgs/layd.jpg'; import CardChanel from './CardChanel'; import IMGBG from '../imgs/rs-bg.png'; import Template from './TemplateWithNavigationForChanel'; import { getChanels } from '../controllers/ChanelController'; class Discovery extends React.Component { constructor() { super(); this.state = { chanels: [] } } componentDidMount() { try { getChanels() .then( res => { if(!res.message) { this.setState( {chanels: res} ) } }); } catch (e) { console.log(e) } } onSubmitFind = event => { event.preventDefault(); let textSearch = document.getElementById("search-chanels"); console.log(textSearch.value); } render() { let { chanels } = this.state; return ( ) } } export default Discovery;
